   Christoph Reimann      : Effective Core Potentials
   Marius Retegan         : Local ZFS, SOC
   Christoph Riplinger    : Optimizer, TS searches, QM/MM, DLPNO-CCSD(T), (RO)-DLPNO pert. Triples
